      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GALLOPING JESSIE (1) had been going along well winning a Grade 5 three back then placing at this track before missing the frame latest when fourth (24.65) at this track. Has the ability and can find winning form this time. ASTON TIMPANA (2) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 24.20 beating Cheer Down. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Deserves serious consideration again. CHILLI CRUMPET (7) was out of the placings last time when seventh at Shepparton (22.64) but scored five back at Shepparton (22.15). Strong form has emerged from her last run. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. DON'T TELL SHELL (6) is new here but should be in the mix.",
